Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Each floor at Solitaire is carefully planned and built with global business techniques and construction procedures. Self-compacting high grade concrete is used for giving the structure impeccable strength while being highly efficient in terms of usable space.The 9600 sq. ft. floor plate is column-less offering a sea-view to all offices. These columns have been cast with M 75 - M 50 grade concrete, making the floor plate even more effective. The floor slabs have been cast with M 40 grade concrete.
